Nevada: Paid QHPs up about 700, total QHPs up 1,500
Tue, 03/04/2014 - 12:04pm
Small update out of Nevada: Between 2/22 and 3/01,paid QHPs went up 698 from 19,142 to 19,840 while unpaid QHPs increased from 7,893 to8,695, for a total increase of 1,500 even.Nevada's Paid percentage remains at around 70%.
Update as of 3/1: 28,535 Nevadans have confirmed Qualified Health Plan selections with Nevada Health Link, 19,840 have paid.
 Nevada Health Link (@NVHealthLink) March 4, 2014
